## Naming Conventions

### Templates
- `kohbo_` prefix for custom dashboard-specific templates
- Generic templates (like `section_title`, `empty_column`) have no prefix
- Descriptive names: `kohbo_device_entity`, `kohbo_thermostat_entity`

### Views/Pages
- Path format: `rooms-<room-name>` (e.g., `rooms-kitchen`)
- Title matches room/page name
- Use `subview: true` for pages not in main navigation

### Entities in Templates
- Use semantic variable names: `[[entity]]`, `[[temperature_sensor]]`, `[[navigation_path]]`
- Group related variables: `[[room_name]]`, `[[room_devices]]`

