## Boolean Toggle Pattern

iOS-style toggle switches use the `kohbo_boolean_entity_layout.yaml` include:

```yaml
- type: entities
  entities:
    - entity: input_boolean.setting_name
      icon: kohbo:kohbo-icon-name
      card_mod: !include /config/dashboards/templates/includes/kohbo_boolean_entity_layout.yaml
      secondary_info: last-changed
      state_color: true
```

